Interface ActivityMvpViewStateDelegateCallback<V extends MvpView,P extends MvpPresenter<V>>

    public interface ActivityMvpViewStateDelegateCallback<V extends MvpView,P extends MvpPresenter<V>>
extends BaseMvpViewStateDelegateCallback<V,P>, ActivityMvpDelegateCallback<V,P>
    An enhanced version of BaseMvpDelegateCallback that adds ViewState support. This interface must be implemented by all (subclasses of) Activity that want to support ViewState and mvp.
